t organization privacy policy about wikipedia disclaimers contact wikipedia developers cookie statement mobile view legal  general  wikipedia legal  general from wikipedia the free encyclopedia   redirected from legal  general group plc jump to navigation search lg redirects here for other uses see lg disambiguation legal  general group plc type public limited company traded as lse lgen ftse  component industry financial services asset management founded   years ago  headquarters london united kingdom key people sir john kingman chairman nigel wilson ceo products life pensions and investments revenue £ billion  operating income £ million  net income £ million  aum £ billion  total equity £ million  website wwwlegalandgeneralgroupcom legal  general group plc commonly known as legal  general is a british multinational financial services company headquartered in london united kingdom its products and services include life insurance general insurance pensions and investment management it has operations in the united kingdom and united states with investment management businesses in the gulf europe and asia legal  general is listed on the london stock exchange and is a constituent of the ftse  index legal  general investment management lgim the asset management arm of lg is the th largest investment management firm in the world by aum it is also the second largest institutional investment management firm in europe after blackrock contents  history   to    to present  operations  senior management  references  external links historyedit  to edit legal  general was formed by sergeant john adams and five other lawyers in june  in a chancery lane coffee shop originally called the new law life assurance society the society was restricted to those in the legal profession the name was changed to legal  general life assurance society to reflect that policies were available to the general public but with share ownership restricted to those in the legal profession the group expand