 provides annuity contracts with guaranteed income for a specified time longevity insurance products for company pension schemes and lifetime mortgages the lgim segment offers index fund management active fixed income and liquidity management solution and liability driven investment active equity and real estate funds the lgc segment provides direct investments with a focus on h legal  general group plc provides various insurance products and services worldwide it operates through legal  general retirement lgr legal  general investment management lgim legal  general capital lgc legal  general insurance lgi savings and general insurance gi segments the lgr segment provides annuity contracts with guaranteed income for a specified time longevity insurance products for company pension schemes and lifetime mortgages the lgim segment offers index fund management active fixed income and liquidity management solution and liability driven investment active equity and real estate funds the lgc segment provides direct investments with a focus on housing infrastructure and sme financing as well as provides investments on treasury and traded assets the lgi segment offers retail and group protection products individual term assurance which provides death benefits universal life contracts including savings and death benefits and unit and index linked savings products bank based investment accounts and corporate pension products the savings segment provides individual and corporate pensions endowment policies withprofits bonds and participating contracts the gi segment offers household and accident sickness unemployment and pet insurance products the company is also involved in treasury institutional fund real estate agency and reinsurance activities in addition it provides property equity mixed asset fixed interest and debt security unit trust products as well as develops building projects and modular housings legal  general group plc was founded in  and is based in london the uni