yers video our full year results our ceo nigel wilson talks about our achievements in  loading the player  legal  general  wikipedia legal  general from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search lg redirects here for other uses see lg disambiguation legal  general group plc type public limited company traded as lse lgen ftse  component industry financial services asset management founded   years ago  headquarters london united kingdom key people sir john kingman chairman nigel wilson ceo products life pensions and investments revenue £ billion  operating income £ million  net income £ million  aum £ billion  total equity £ million  website wwwlegalandgeneralgroupcom legal  general group plc commonly known as legal  general is a british multinational financial services company headquartered in london united kingdom its products and services include life insurance general insurance pensions and investment management it has operations in the united kingdom and united states with investment management businesses in the gulf europe and asia legal  general is listed on the london stock exchange and is a constituent of the ftse  index legal  general investment management lgim the asset management arm of lg is the th largest investment management firm in the world by aum it is also the second largest institutional investment management firm in europe after blackrock contents  history   to    to present  operations  senior management  references  external links historyedit  to edit legal  general was formed by sergeant john adams and five other lawyers in june  in a chancery lane coffee shop originally called the new law life assurance society the society was restricted to those in the legal profession the name was changed to legal  general life assurance society to reflect that policies were available to the general public but with share ownership restricted to those in the legal profession the group expanded in the uk and soon began to acquire overseas life assurance companies purchasing a pensions business from the metropolitan life assurance company of new york in the s the society became a wholly owned division of legal  general group plc in the s it bought government employee life insurance from geico in the usa renamed banner life and the dutch branch of unlike assurance group and also set up business in france during the s the former legal  general logo entrance to legal  generals offices furze hill kingswood in the s the main office of legal  general was moved from temple bar house in the city of london to a remodelled former girls school in leafy kingswood surrey save for some top management functions which remained in london the girls school st monicas which formed the basis for the site was attended by the novelist vera brittain mother of the politician shirley williams the kingswood site which included sports fields a park a large and luxurious swimming pool a canteen and a simulacrum of an english pub among other facilities was expanded in the s and again in the s in  it was announced that the headquarters would close potentially before  in fact after a period of uncertainty for the staff at kingswood it was announced that the site would shut much earlier in  the previous legal  general logo incorporates the image of the temple bar which is still used in the logo of the companys social and athletic committee and the founding date the umbrella logo used today was introduced by former chief press officer gordon macdonald in june  between  and  legal and general sponsored the regional weather forecasts for the itv network and in  legal  general announced plans which never came to fruition to merge its business with national westminster bank to form the first bancassurance company in the uk  to presentedit the company sold the legal  general bank and legal  general mortgage services to northern rock in  and sold its stake in gresham insurance its joint venture with barclays bank to barclays in  in  legal  general bought suffolk life a provider of self invested pension products sold suffolk life in  and also outsourced its it development areas to tcs tata consultancy services the company formed a joint venture with two indian public sector banks bank of baroda and andhra bank to launch indiafirst life insurance company in india in  and outsourced some it areas to ibm in october  in  the company formed legal  general reinsurance a bermudianbased reinsurance company legal  general re completed its maiden external transaction in the dutch market in cooperation with hannover re in december  legal  general has expanded its operations in the last five years taking over lucida life in  and acquiring the £ billion uk annuity portfolio of aegon in  since  the company has sought out better returns on its annuity and shareholder funds by committing to invest £ billion in uk infrastructure projects such as urban regeneration housing clean energy and small business finance this has involved the group partnering with many financial organisations including the dutch pension fund pggm and pemberton asset management operationsedit the company offers a wide range of products for individuals and corporate businesses its investment management is the uk’s largest investment manager of uk pension fund assets and has a growing us business based in chicago illinois legal  general’s core business focuses upon helping companies provide pension benefits for employees as well as being one of the uk’s largest providers of autoenrolled pension pensions with over  million customers the group also helps companies with defined benefit pension schemes meet their liabilities through investment strategies and even taking over the liability to pay company pensions legal  general’s life insurance business is the uk’s largest providing cover for both individuals and companies the group is seeking to expand its life insurance businesses in the us and india legal  general is planning to help provide solutions for the uk’s housing shortage through its investments in building new homes to buy and to rent the company’s range of construction initiatives includes establishing a pioneering hightech modular housing factory in yorkshire senior managementedit in the s and early s ron peet a sociallyconscious actuary was ceo of legal  general having previously headed its australian operation peet helped the campaign for thalidomide children legal  general then owning a large bloc of shares  million in distillers dr nigel wilson the previous cfo became group chief executive on  june  he succeeded tim breedon who had been ceo since  january  and who was paid an annual salary of £ other senior management include jeff davies group chief financial officer mark zinkula ceo of legal  general investment management the investment management arm of the firm and kerrigan procter ceo of the group’s retirement business together with nigel wilson they form legal  generals executive board referencesedit  a b c d e f g preliminary results  pdf retrieved  april    httpswwwipecomreportsspecialreportstopassetmanagerstopassetmanagersglobalassetsnowtrnarticle  httpswwwipecomanalysisanalysisblackrockdominatesaslgimjoinslargestmanagerswwwipecomanalysisanalysisblackrockdominatesaslgimjoinslargestmanagersfullarticle  a b legal  general milestones –  a b legal  general milestones –  vera brittains testament of youth essential surrey  january  retrieved  april    general legal  legal  general  kingswood office wwwlegalandgeneralgroupcom retrieved    legal and general to leave kingswood site surrey mirror retrieved    hundreds could lose jobs in legal and general kingswood closure bbc news retrieved    chapple james job numbers simply do not add up says unite union getsurrey retrieved    lg delays kingswood office closure amid strike plans  ftadvisercom wwwftadvisercom retrieved    buerkle tom  september  bankassurance comes to britain international herald tribune retrieved  april    why northern rock is music